  "description": "feliX stripped to near-silence. snap intensity at minimum, long decay, pitchLock on — the neon tetra holds its position in the water column. A ghost of a tone, barely audible, filter mostly closed. The school (unison) is just two voices at 6-cent detune, enough to create mild beating but not presence. Complement to OddOscar's Dark Thread and Cave Breath.",
